
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Main as main.py (FastAPI App)
    participant Middleware as RequestLoggingMiddleware
    participant AuthRouter
    participant UsersRouter
    participant ItemsRouter
    participant AuthService
    participant UserService
    participant ItemService
    participant UserRepo as UserRepository
    participant ItemRepo as ItemRepository
    participant Security
    participant Logger as AppLogger
    participant DB as Database (AsyncSession)

    Note over Main: Application Startup
    Main->>DB: init_db()
    DB-->>Main: tables created
    Main->>Main: add_middleware(RequestLoggingMiddleware)
    Main->>Main: include_router(auth_router, prefix=/api/v1)
    Main->>Main: include_router(users_router, prefix=/api/v1)
    Main->>Main: include_router(items_router, prefix=/api/v1)
    Main->>Main: add_exception_handlers(AppException, ValidationError, HTTPException)
    Main->>Logger: 初始化 AppLogger

    Note over Client, DB: GET /health - 健康檢查
    Client->>Main: GET /health
    Main->>DB: 檢查資料庫連線狀態
    DB-->>Main: 連線正常
    Main-->>Client: HealthResponse {status: ok, version, database: connected, timestamp}

    Note over Client, DB: 請求中介層處理流程
    Client->>Middleware: 任意 HTTP 請求
    Middleware->>Logger: log_request(method, path, request_id)
    Middleware->>Main: call_next(request)
    Main-->>Middleware: response
    Middleware->>Logger: log_request(method, path, status_code, duration)
    Middleware-->>Client: response

    Note over Client, DB: POST /api/v1/auth/login - 使用者登入
    Client->>AuthRouter: POST /api/v1/auth/login {username, password}
    AuthRouter->>DB: get_db()
    DB-->>AuthRouter: db session
    AuthRouter->>UserRepo: __init__(db)
    AuthRouter->>AuthService: __init__(user_repo)
    AuthRouter->>AuthService: login(login_data)
    AuthService->>UserRepo: get_by_username(username)
    UserRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username=?
    DB-->>UserRepo: UserModel
    UserRepo-->>AuthService: UserModel
    AuthService->>Security: verify_password(password, hashed_password)
    Security-->>AuthService: True
    AuthService->>Security: create_access_token({sub: username})
    Security-->>AuthService: JWT token string
    AuthService-->>AuthRouter: TokenSchema
    AuthRouter-->>Client: StandardResponse {status: success, data: {access_token, token_type}, message: 登入成功}

    Note over Client, DB: GET /api/v1/auth/me - 取得當前使用者資訊
    Client->>AuthRouter: GET /api/v1/auth/me (Bearer token)
    AuthRouter->>Security: decode_access_token(token)
    Security-->>AuthRouter: {sub: username}
    AuthRouter->>UserRepo: get_by_username(username)
    UserRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username=?
    DB-->>UserRepo: UserModel
    UserRepo-->>AuthRouter: UserModel (current_user)
    AuthRouter-->>Client: StandardResponse {status: success, data: UserResponse}

    Note over Client, DB: POST /api/v1/users - 建立新使用者
    Client->>UsersRouter: POST /api/v1/users {username, email, password}
    UsersRouter->>DB: get_db()
    DB-->>UsersRouter: db session
    UsersRouter->>UserRepo: __init__(db)
    UsersRouter->>UserService: __init__(user_repo)
    UsersRouter->>UserService: create_user(user_data)
    UserService->>UserRepo: get_by_email(email)
    UserRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE email=?
    DB-->>UserRepo: None
    UserRepo-->>UserService: None
    UserService->>UserRepo: get_by_username(username)
    UserRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username=?
    DB-->>UserRepo: None
    UserRepo-->>UserService: None
    UserService->>Security: get_password_hash(password)
    Security-->>UserService: hashed_password
    UserService->>UserRepo: create({username, email, hashed_password})
    UserRepo->>DB: INSERT INTO users VALUES (...)
    DB-->>UserRepo: UserModel
    UserRepo-->>UserService: UserModel
    UserService-->>UsersRouter: UserResponse
    UsersRouter-->>Client: StandardResponse {status: success, data: UserResponse, message: 使用者建立成功, status_code: 201}

    Note over Client, DB: GET /api/v1/users - 取得所有使用者
    Client->>UsersRouter: GET /api/v1/users?skip=0&limit=10
    UsersRouter->>UserService: get_users(skip, limit)
    UserService->>UserRepo: get_all(skip, limit)
    UserRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM users LIMIT ? OFFSET ?
    DB-->>UserRepo: List[UserModel]
    UserRepo-->>UserService: List[UserModel]
    UserService-->>UsersRouter: List[UserResponse]
    UsersRouter-->>Client: StandardResponse {status: success, data: [UserResponse]}

    Note over Client, DB: GET /api/v1/users/{user_id} - 取得特定使用者
    Client->>UsersRouter: GET /api/v1/users/1
    UsersRouter->>UserService: get_user(user_id=1)
    UserService->>UserRepo: get_by_id(user_id=1)
    UserRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE id=1
    DB-->>UserRepo: UserModel or None
    UserRepo-->>UserService: UserModel
    UserService-->>UsersRouter: UserResponse
    UsersRouter-->>Client: StandardResponse {status: success, data: UserResponse}

    Note over Client, DB: PUT /api/v1/users/{user_id} - 更新使用者 (需驗證)
    Client->>UsersRouter: PUT /api/v1/users/1 {username} (Bearer token)
    UsersRouter->>Security: decode_access_token(token)
    Security-->>UsersRouter: current_user
    UsersRouter->>UserService: update_user(user_id=1, user_data, current_user)
    UserService->>UserService: 驗證 current_user.id == user_id 或 is_superuser
    UserService->>UserRepo: update(user_id=1, user_data)
    UserRepo->>DB: UPDATE users SET ... WHERE id=1
    DB-->>UserRepo: UserModel
    UserRepo-->>UserService: UserModel
    UserService-->>UsersRouter: UserResponse
    UsersRouter-->>Client: StandardResponse {status: success, data: UserResponse}

    Note over Client, DB: DELETE /api/v1/users/{user_id} - 刪除使用者 (需驗證)
    Client->>UsersRouter: DELETE /api/v1/users/1 (Bearer token)
    UsersRouter->>Security: decode_access_token(token)
    Security-->>UsersRouter: current_user
    UsersRouter->>UserService: delete_user(user_id=1, current_user)
    UserService->>UserService: 驗證 current_user.id == user_id 或 is_superuser
    UserService->>UserRepo: delete(user_id=1)
    UserRepo->>DB: DELETE FROM users WHERE id=1
    DB-->>UserRepo: True
    UserRepo-->>UserService: True
    UserService-->>UsersRouter: True
    UsersRouter-->>Client: StandardResponse {status: success, message: 使用者已刪除}

    Note over Client, DB: POST /api/v1/items - 建立 Item (需驗證)
    Client->>ItemsRouter: POST /api/v1/items {title, description} (Bearer token)
    ItemsRouter->>Security: decode_access_token(token)
    Security-->>ItemsRouter: current_user
    ItemsRouter->>ItemRepo: __init__(db)
    ItemsRouter->>ItemService: __init__(item_repo)
    ItemsRouter->>ItemService: create_item(item_data, owner_id=current_user.id)
    ItemService->>ItemRepo: create({title, description, owner_id})
    ItemRepo->>DB: INSERT INTO items VALUES (...)
    DB-->>ItemRepo: ItemModel
    ItemRepo-->>ItemService: ItemModel
    ItemService-->>ItemsRouter: ItemResponse
    ItemsRouter-->>Client: StandardResponse {status: success, data: ItemResponse, status_code: 201}

    Note over Client, DB: GET /api/v1/items/me - 取得自己的 Items (需驗證)
    Client->>ItemsRouter: GET /api/v1/items/me?skip=0&limit=10 (Bearer token)
    ItemsRouter->>Security: decode_access_token(token)
    Security-->>ItemsRouter: current_user
    ItemsRouter->>ItemService: get_my_items(owner_id=current_user.id, skip, limit)
    ItemService->>ItemRepo: get_by_owner(owner_id, skip, limit)
    ItemRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM items WHERE owner_id=? LIMIT ? OFFSET ?
    DB-->>ItemRepo: List[ItemModel]
    ItemRepo-->>ItemService: List[ItemModel]
    ItemService-->>ItemsRouter: List[ItemResponse]
    ItemsRouter-->>Client: StandardResponse {status: success, data: [ItemResponse]}

    Note over Client, DB: 全域錯誤處理流程
    Client->>UsersRouter: GET /api/v1/users/999
    UsersRouter->>UserService: get_user(user_id=999)
    UserService->>UserRepo: get_by_id(user_id=999)
    UserRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE id=999
    DB-->>UserRepo: None
    UserRepo-->>UserService: None
    UserService->>UserService: raise AppException(404, NOT_FOUND, 使用者不存在)
    UserService-->>Main: AppException
    Main->>Logger: log_error(AppException, context)
    Main-->>Client: {status: error, error_code: NOT_FOUND, detail: 使用者不存在, message: 請求失敗, status_code: 404}

    Note over Client, DB: 測試流程 (pytest + httpx)
    participant TestClient as AsyncClient (tests)
    participant Conftest as conftest.py
    Conftest->>DB: 建立 SQLite 測試資料庫
    Conftest->>DB: override_get_db()
    Conftest->>UserRepo: 建立測試使用者
    Conftest->>ItemRepo: 建立測試 Item
    Conftest->>Security: 生成測試用 JWT Token
    TestClient->>Main: POST /api/v1/auth/login
    Main-->>TestClient: TokenSchema
    TestClient->>Main: GET /api/v1/users (Bearer token)
    Main-->>TestClient: StandardResponse
    Conftest->>DB: 清除測試資料
